    <!-- Design notes -->
    <mxCell id="60" value="Design Notes:&#xa;• High Cohesion: All operations relate to user lifecycle management&#xa;• Controlled Coupling: depends only on UserRepository and SecurityContext&#xa;• IUserService interface decouples controller from implementation (testability)&#xa;• role-based access enforced via SecurityContext (QG-5 Security)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#999999;fillColor=#f5f5f5;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
